WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.240
Welcome to Learn with AI in

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:03.040
Tominets.

00:00:03.260 --> 00:00:06.700
Quick concept, Simple Metafers and Zero Jargon

00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:07.500
Overloop.

00:00:07.920 --> 00:00:09.440
AI Machine Learning Deep

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:10.240
Learning.

00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:11.420
People use these three

00:00:11.420 --> 00:00:12.280
interchangeably.

00:00:12.780 --> 00:00:13.580
What's the

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:13.880
difference?

00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:17.080
Picture three Russian nesting balls that we

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:18.260
have played with while we were

00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:19.060
young.

00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:21.160
The biggest doll is the artificial

00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:21.960
intelligence.

00:00:22.520 --> 00:00:24.700
Any system that mimics smart

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:25.500
behavior.

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:29.700
Just bots, recommendation engine, chat bots, all

00:00:29.700 --> 00:00:30.500
AI.

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:33.200
Inside that sets machine

00:00:33.200 --> 00:00:34.000
learning.

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:36.720
AI that learns from the data instead

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:37.900
of hard coded

00:00:37.900 --> 00:00:38.700
rules.

00:00:38.840 --> 00:00:41.640
Spotify learning your taste of music, that

00:00:41.640 --> 00:00:42.440
is

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:42.720
ML.

00:00:43.020 --> 00:00:46.560
Inside ML sets the smallest doll, deep

00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:47.360
learning.

00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:50.320
ML using neural network with many

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:51.160
layers.

00:00:51.860 --> 00:00:55.820
Chat GPT, image generator, voice recognition, that

00:00:55.820 --> 00:00:56.620
is deep

00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:57.240
learning.

00:00:56.840 --> 00:01:00.600
So every deep learning system is machine

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:01.400
learning.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:04.519
Every ML system is AI, but not

00:01:04.519 --> 00:01:08.280
all AI uses ML and not all

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.580
ML is deep

00:01:09.580 --> 00:01:10.380
learning.

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.440
Three terms, one nested

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:13.240
family.

00:01:13.620 --> 00:01:15.260
Remember, AI is the big

00:01:15.260 --> 00:01:16.060
umbrella.

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:17.980
Machine learning learns from the

00:01:17.980 --> 00:01:18.780
data.

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:20.880
Deep learning uses layer neural

00:01:20.880 --> 00:01:21.680
networks.

00:01:22.180 --> 00:01:23.900
All of them are nested, but not

00:01:23.900 --> 00:01:24.700
interchangeable.

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:26.060
That's your concept for the

00:01:26.060 --> 00:01:26.860
day.

00:01:26.820 --> 00:01:28.360
Follow for the next one, learn AI

00:01:28.360 --> 00:01:29.220
in two

00:01:29.220 --> 00:01:30.020
minutes.

